Invocation Name: the flipside radio
des: An 80's music station that's the perfect destination for anyone who loves the music of the decade that brought us big hair,neon colors and MTV. You'll hear all the hits the era as well as lesser known gems,so you'll discover new favorites as well as sing along to the songs you already know and love.Tune in and let the nostalgia wash over you. We will also play tunes from other decades as well as current hits! Catch you on The Flipside!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
